Footage of a Gambian man drowning in Italy while onlookers laughed and made racist comments has gone viral on social media.People can be heard shouting things (in Italian) such as:&#8220;He is stupid. He wants to die.&#8221;&#8220;Go on, go back home,&#8221;Life rings were thrown to the man but he ignored them, causing rumours and speculation that this was a suicide.